title: Episode 157: Toes & Holes (Feat. Estelle)
itunes:title: Episode 157: Toes & Holes (Feat. Estelle)
description:
Singer Estelle joins the ladies of Lip Service this week and shares how her parents love story inspired her latest album. Estelle goes on to explain what some of her major red flags are, getting better sexually with age, experimenting, and much more! Lore'l even confesses to peeing on her ex...enjoy!
